It is a good idea to fortify 1 or 2 servings with added Field of Greens or Green Vibrance green food powders.* Day 2 You can have unlimited amounts of fruit and vegetable juices; and warm vegetable broth. Again; fortification with Field of Greens or Green Vibrance enhances replenishment of key nutrients.* Day 3 You may begin eating whole fruits and vegetables and unlimited vegetable broth.* Days 4-10 Now you are ready to introduce other food sources. You will drink 6-8 glasses of Vibrant Cleanse per day. You can have unlimited amounts of water; and herbal tea. You can stay on the cleanse for as little as 3 days and up to 30 days.
